sentences: Only downside : three entrees served simultaneously but fourth ( beet/ goat cheese ravioli ) was 2 - 3 minutes later which allowed my accompaniments ( delicious creamy polenta ) to cool off to much .
50$ for buffet and mind you i only ate crab legs
The staff is always friendly and they make you feel comfortable even when you're getting uncomfortable work done.
Everyone is kind and professional, with no pretense.
there is no sense of urgency of your time at all
